        <num>CC 1284</num>
        <heading>1284.  Donation of movables as absolute transfer of rights</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1284.  Donation of movables as absolute transfer of rights.
Therefore the donation of movables contains an absolute transfer of the rights of the donor to the donee in the movables thus given.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=108634</p>
